trans-unit.source: Represents a rectangle annotation.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et rektangel merknad.

trans-unit.source: A rectangle annotation can display text inside the rectangle, in addition to being displayed as a rectangle only.
trans-unit.target: Merknad med et rektangel kan vise tekst i rektanglet, i tillegg til å vises som et rektangel bare.

trans-unit.source: So you can annotate using a rectangle or a rectangle with text inside it.
trans-unit.target: Så du kan legge til merknader i et rektangel og et rektangel med teksten i den.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPathPoint"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPathPoint"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the annotation type.
trans-unit.target: Henter merknadstypen.

trans-unit.source: For internal use, should not be used.
trans-unit.target: For intern bruk, kan ikke brukes.

trans-unit.source: The annotation type.
trans-unit.target: Merknadstypen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the background color of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir bakgrunnsfargen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value used to draw the annotation background.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne bakgrunnsfargen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the gradient style of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir gradering stilen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: Two colors are used to draw the gradient, a primary color that is specified the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackColor%2A> and a secondary color that is specified with the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackSecondaryColor%2A>.
trans-unit.target: To farger brukes til å tegne graderingen, en primær farge som er angitt <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackColor%2A>, og en sekundær farge som er angitt med <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackSecondaryColor%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackSecondaryColor%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.GradientStyle"></xref> value used to draw an annotation background.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.GradientStyle"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne merknadsbakgrunnen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the hatch style of an annotation background.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir skraveringsstilen for merknadsbakgrunnen.

trans-unit.source: Two colors are used to draw the hatching, a primary color that is specified the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackColor%2A> property, and a secondary color that is specified with the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackColor%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: To farger brukes til å tegne skravering, en primær farge som er angitt i <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackColor%2A>egenskapen og en sekundær farge som er angitt med den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackColor%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackColor%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartHatchStyle"></xref> value used to draw the background.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartHatchStyle"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne bakgrunnen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the secondary color for an annotation background.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den sekundære fargen for merknadsbakgrunnen.

trans-unit.source: This color is used with <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackColor%2A> when the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackHatchStyle%2A> or <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackGradientStyle%2A> property is used.
trans-unit.target: Denne fargen brukes med <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackColor%2A>når den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackHatchStyle%2A>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackGradientStyle%2A>egenskapen brukes.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackGradientStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackHatchStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation.BackColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value used to draw the annotation background with hatching or gradient fill.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne merknadsbakgrunnen skravering eller gradering fyll.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the line color of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir linjefargen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value used to draw the annotation line.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne merknadslinjen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the line style of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir linjestilen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartDashStyle"></xref> value used to draw the line style of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartDashStyle"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne linjestilen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the line width, in pixels, of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir linjetykkelse, på en merknad i piksler.

trans-unit.source: An <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""></xref> value that represents the line width, in pixels.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""> </xref> verdi som Representer linjetykkelse i piksler.
